section.section:
Except as provided in subsection (b) of this section, this subtitle applies to:
property insurance;
casualty insurance;
surety insurance;
marine insurance; and
wet marine and transportation insurance.

text.section:
This subtitle does not apply to:
reinsurance, except as provided in § 11-222 of this subtitle;
insurance of vessels or craft or their cargoes, marine protection and indemnity insurance, or insurance of other risks commonly insured under policies of marine insurance, as distinguished from inland marine insurance;
insurance against loss of or damage to aircraft including their accessories and equipment, or insurance against liability, other than workers' compensation insurance or employer's liability insurance, arising out of the ownership, maintenance, or use of aircraft;
title insurance; or
Chesapeake Employers' Insurance Company.
